=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 澳洲jj"},{"pid":"abaa1e266b4c23f2d7ef822a11f738598ed19155","tid":314343,"uid":60967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實外國生活真係唔悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能因為我中學就過左黎 所以喺high school識到好多朋友<br />\n<br />\n而家每個weekend 都有house party <br />\n<br />\n平日放左學又會成班frd去踢下波 篤下波咁<br />\n<br />\n放長假又會去下road trip <br />\n<br />\n我都唔明點解啲人會話外國生活悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 澳洲jj</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部份人都唔係中學就過去<br />\n有啲做野比人調過去乜圍子都冇真係會好悶"},{"pid":"fe9c6ab3321da26c39b49366187d60e9eda47c57","tid":314343,"uid":41461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實外國生活真係唔悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能因為我中學就過左黎 所以喺high school識到好多朋友<br />\n<br />\n而家每個weekend 都有house party <br />\n<br />\n平日放左學又會成班frd去踢下波 篤下波咁<br />\n<br />\n放長假又會去下road trip <br />\n<br />\n我都唔明點解啲人會話外國生活悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 澳洲jj</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部份人都唔係中學就過去<br />\n有啲做野比人調過去乜圍子都冇真係會好悶</blockquote><br />\n我都覺 我識好多以前既中學同學 DSE衰左先過黎 然後完全埋唔到local堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f77853dfd58633c290ec369922649df8eeeb2e","tid":314343,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"Town仔我都住過，最識到friend同你一齊癲，其實大撚把野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166e027aee18bc677a77992b613761eae3a1ccad","tid":314343,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"香港勝在夠細，要出旺角行街睇戲、定係蒲蘭桂坊、定係去南生圍睇風景，都係30分鐘至1個鐘車程<br />\n<b